title: My Experience at the Good Morning America Block Party 2017 with Dierks Bentley
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: Mary I'm so sorry for this. It's very sad. I hope your daughter is okay. She doesn't deserve this, but at least she saw how caring and protecting her mother is! I'm proud of you! Have a nice day!
Mary, did your neighbors wonder where you were when they were on the lawn?
